    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/73af0f6e4a707a15f2cf24f47dd16a8d.poster.avif?t=1764461568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/73af0f6e4a707a15f2cf24f47dd16a8d.webm?t=1764461568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/73af0f6e4a707a15f2cf24f47dd16a8d.mp4?t=1764461568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience the First Chapter of the Adventure</strong><br>Step into the strange, futuristic city of North Terrace where danger lurks at every turn. In this gripping 30-minute demo, Evo finds himself at a breaking point. His unhinged landlord demands he pay his overdue rent or face dire consequences. Can a job interview at a seedy tech startup turn his luck around, or does his therapist hold the key to his survival? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meanwhile, the city of North Terrace is under siege by a surge of terrifying Negative Agents. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Evo find a way out, or will the city consume him?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the tension and unravel the mystery—play the demo now.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/9cfe8858c7de34183148f19018ba31b5.poster.avif?t=1764461568\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/9cfe8858c7de34183148f19018ba31b5.webm?t=1764461568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/9cfe8858c7de34183148f19018ba31b5.mp4?t=1764461568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What You’ll Do in the Demo:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drive Through the Wasteland:</strong> Navigate the eerie, bullet-scarred streets of North Terrace in your hover truck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wander Mysterious Spaces:</strong> Explore Evo’s unsettling apartment, where every detail hints at a deeper mystery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interact with Characters: </strong>Meet your therapist Dr. Cid, AJ the goth, her boss the CEO, and many more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face Danger in the Dark:</strong> Confront shadowy enemies in a tense nighttime encounter at the water treatment plant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/08eebf4c0c7b71d3fbb5354ec75d9263.poster.avif?t=1764461568\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/08eebf4c0c7b71d3fbb5354ec75d9263.webm?t=1764461568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/08eebf4c0c7b71d3fbb5354ec75d9263.mp4?t=1764461568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive third-person exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tense, unpredictable enemy encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic character and environmental interactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A haunting, original soundtrack</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/141168402f76abc18fdc3ab0325be86a.poster.avif?t=1764461568\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/141168402f76abc18fdc3ab0325be86a.webm?t=1764461568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379320/extras/141168402f76abc18fdc3ab0325be86a.mp4?t=1764461568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Add Alter Evo to your Wishlist today and leave a review on the demo page to help improve the full game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Content Warning:</strong> Demo contains blood, violence, and suggestive themes that are not appropriate for children.</p>",
